      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, im 5 months pregnant and i have such a bad sinus infection... my head is pounding and i cant breathe through my nose at all. i have some Sudafed (pseudoephedrine) in my cabinet from before, is it okay to take that for the congestion or is it risky for the baby?",
