      "content": "wait, ibuprofen? i thought you weren't supposed to take that while pregnant? my midwife told me to avoid it. also the steam thing isnt really helping the pain... if i really cant wait until morning to call the doctor, can i just take a standard dose of the Sudafed to get some sleep? it's just one pill, it shouldn't hurt anything right?",
